            </div>
            
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🚗</div>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Custom Vehicles</h3>
                    <p class="feature-description">Over 500 custom vehicles including supercars, motorcycles, emergency vehicles, and unique imports you won't find anywhere else.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🏢</div>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Business System</h3>
                    <p class="feature-description">Own and operate legitimate businesses, from car dealerships to restaurants. Build your empire and create jobs for other players.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">👮</div>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Realistic Police</h3>
                    <p class="feature-description">Advanced police systems with realistic procedures, court cases, and a justice system that creates compelling criminal vs law storylines.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🏠</div>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Housing & Properties</h3>
                    <p class="feature-description">Buy, sell, and customize properties. From luxury penthouses to gang hideouts, make Unrestricted your home.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">💊</div>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Drug System</h3>
                    <p class="feature-description">Complex drug manufacturing and distribution system with territories, rivalries, and high-stakes criminal enterprises.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🎭</div>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Character Development</h3>
                    <p class="feature-description">Deep character progression system with skills, reputation, and relationships that matter. Your choices shape your story.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Jobs Section -->
    <section class="jobs reveal" id="jobs">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
