                <p class="section-subtitle">From law enforcement to criminal enterprises, find your role in Unrestricted</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="jobs-grid">
                <div class="job-card">
                    <div class="job-icon">👮‍♂️</div>
                    <h3 class="job-title">Police Officer</h3>
                    <p class="job-description">Protect and serve the citizens of Unrestricted. Investigate crimes, make arrests, and maintain order in the city.</p>
                    <div class="job-salary">£2,500 - £4,500/hour</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="job-card">
                    <div class="job-icon">🚑</div>
                    <h3 class="job-title">UHS Paramedic</h3>
                    <p class="job-description">Save lives and provide medical assistance. Respond to emergencies and keep the city healthy.</p>
                    <div class="job-salary">£2,000 - £3,500/hour</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="job-card">
                    <div class="job-icon">⚖️</div>
                    <h3 class="job-title">Lawyer</h3>
                    <p class="job-description">Defend clients in court, negotiate deals, and navigate the complex legal system of Unrestricted.</p>
                    <div class="job-salary">£3,000 - £6,000/hour</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="job-card">
                    <div class="job-icon">🔧</div>
                    <h3 class="job-title">Mechanic</h3>
                    <p class="job-description">Fix and customize vehicles for the city's residents. Run your own garage or work for established shops.</p>
                    <div class="job-salary">£1,800 - £3,200/hour</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="job-card">
                    <div class="job-icon">🚚</div>
                    <h3 class="job-title">Delivery Driver</h3>
                    <p class="job-description">Transport goods across the city. From legal deliveries to more questionable cargo operations.</p>
                    <div class="job-salary">£1,500 - £2,800/hour</div>
                </div>

                <div class="job-card">
                    <div class="job-icon">🏪</div>
                    <h3 class="job-title">Store Owner</h3>
                    <p class="job-description">Run your own retail business. Stock inventory, serve customers, and build your commercial empire.</p>
                    <div class="job-salary">£2,200 - £4,000/hour</div>
                </div>

                <div class="job-card">
                    <div class="job-icon">🚖</div>
                    <h3 class="job-title">Taxi</h3>
                    <p class="job-description">Pick up and transport passengers across the city while earning money for each trip.</p>
                    <div class="job-salary">£2,200 - £4,000/hour</div>
                </div>

                <div class="job-card">
                    <div class="job-icon">⛏️</div>
                    <h3 class="job-title">Mining</h3>
                    <p class="job-description">Head to the mines to extract valuable ores and materials that can be sold or refined.</p>
                    <div class="job-salary">£1,800 - £3,500/hour</div>
                </div>

                <div class="job-card">
                    <div class="job-icon">🎪</div>
                    <h3 class="job-title">Criminal</h3>
                    <p class="job-description">Choose the life of crime. Rob banks, run illegal operations, but beware of the consequences.</p>
                    <div class="job-salary">£??? - High Risk/Reward</div>
                </div>
                
            </div>
        </div>
