   <!-- FAQ Section -->
   <section class="faq reveal" id="faq">
       <div class="container">
           <div class="section-header">
               <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
               <p class="section-subtitle">Everything you need to know about joining Unrestricted RP</p>
           </div>
           
           <div class="faq-container">
               <div class="faq-item">
                   <div class="faq-question">
                       <span>How do I join the server?</span>
                       <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                   </div>
                   <div class="faq-answer">
                       <p>Simply click the "Connect" button on our homepage or use the server code "jyrm3l" in FiveM. Make sure you have FiveM installed and join our Discord for whitelist information if required.</p>
                   </div>
               </div>
               
               <div class="faq-item">
                   <div class="faq-question">
                       <span>Do I need to be whitelisted?</span>
                       <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                   </div>
                   <div class="faq-answer">
                       <p>Check our Discord server for current whitelist requirements. Some roles may require applications, but general access is typically open to all players who follow our rules.</p>
                   </div>
               </div>
               
               <div class="faq-item">
                   <div class="faq-question">
                       <span>What are the server requirements?</span>
                       <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                   </div>
                   <div class="faq-answer">
                       <p>You need a legal copy of GTA V, FiveM installed, a working microphone for voice chat, and a stable internet connection. We recommend at least 8GB RAM for optimal performance.</p>
                   </div>
               </div>
               
               <div class="faq-item">
                   <div class="faq-question">
                       <span>Can I play as a criminal?</span>
                       <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                   </div>
                   <div class="faq-answer">
                       <p>Absolutely! We support both legal and criminal roleplay. You can run businesses, join gangs, participate in heists, or pursue a life of crime - just remember to roleplay realistically and follow server rules.</p>
                   </div>
               </div>
               
               <div class="faq-item">
                   <div class="faq-question">
                       <span>How do I apply for police or EMS?</span>
                       <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                   </div>
                   <div class="faq-answer">
                       <p>Join our Discord server and check the applications channel. You will need to fill out an application form and may need to attend an interview. Make sure you meet the minimum playtime requirements.</p>
                   </div>
               </div>
               
               <div class="faq-item">
                   <div class="faq-question">
                       <span>Is there an age requirement?</span>
                       <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                   </div>
                   <div class="faq-answer">
                       <p>Yes, players must be at least 16 years old to join our server. This ensures mature roleplay and helps maintain a respectful community environment.</p>
                   </div>
               </div>
           </div>
       </div>
   </section>

